FLAG --format=WORD : Set the output format.

    This flag is basically the long (but more readable) way
    of using flags like -l and -C.

--format=across

    Equivalent to "-x"

--format=commas

    Equivalent to "-m"

--format=horizontal

    Equivalent to "-x"

--format=long

    Equivalent to "-l"

--format=single-column

    Equivalent to "-1"

--format=verbose

    Equivalent to "-l"

--format=vertical

    Equivalent to "-C"
